OL,3,CTwo British hikers found alive but
OL,4,Cbadly burned after wildfires in south
OL,5,CSpain
OL,7,FTwo British hikers have been found
OL,8,Falive but badly burned following
OL,9,Fdeadly wildfires that have hit
OL,10,Fsouthern Spain.
OL,12,FThe man and woman, who have not been
OL,13,Fidentified, are thought to have
OL,14,Fsuffered 40% burns, according to
OL,15,FSpanish national broadcaster, RTVE.
OL,17,FThe pair were discovered by a team of
OL,18,FCivil Guards, who said they had
OL,19,Falready checked the area, but had a
OL,20,Ffeeling that they should go back.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
