PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1783878540
OL,3,CTwo British hikers found alive but
OL,4,Cbadly burned after wildfires in south
OL,5,CSpain
OL,7,FAt least 12 people are believed to
OL,8,Fhave died in the fire near the village
OL,9,Fof Bedar, in Almeria province.
OL,11,FAt least four are thought to be
OL,12,FBritish, after four bodies were found
OL,13,Fin a burnt-out car with its steering
OL,14,Fwheel on the right.
OL,16,FIn an interview with RTVE, the Civil
OL,17,FGuard officers said they found the two
OL,18,FBritish people alive just as night was
OL,19,Ffalling.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
