CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1783878540
OL,3,CTwo British hikers found alive but
OL,4,Cbadly burned after wildfires in south
OL,5,CSpain
OL,7,FSergeant Pedro Barre told the
OL,8,Fbroadcaster: "That experience we
OL,9,Faccumulate over the years is what
OL,10,Ftells you: take another look, give it
OL,11,Fone last try, check again just in
OL,12,Fcase."
OL,14,FHe said they called out and used
OL,15,Fwhistles, before eventually hearing a
OL,16,Fsound which they thought at first
OL,17,Fcould have been an echo.
OL,26,@pD@NOUtD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
