OL,3,CTwo British hikers found alive but
OL,4,Cbadly burned after wildfires in south
OL,5,CSpain
OL,7,FAnother of the rescuers, Rafael Zea,
OL,8,Fsaid that given the couple's injuries
OL,9,Fit must have taken a "Titanic effort"
OL,10,Ffor them to raise their voices to be
OL,11,Fheard.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,FWith the help of firefighters and
OL,19,Femergency services, they were rescued
OL,20,Fafter more than two hours.
OL,26,@qD@VOUqD@eO]
