OL,3,CTwo British hikers found alive but
OL,4,Cbadly burned after wildfires in south
OL,5,CSpain
OL,7,FThe pair are now said to be in a
OL,8,Fserious condition in hospital,
OL,9,Falthough their lives are not believed
OL,10,Fto be in danger.
OL,12,FSpanish authorities believe all the
OL,13,Fvictims were foreign tourists, who are
OL,14,Fthought to have attempted to escape on
OL,15,Ffoot after apparently abandoning their
OL,16,Fvehicles and trying to flee through
OL,17,Frugged terrain.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
