OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1783878540
OL,3,CTwo British hikers found alive but
OL,4,Cbadly burned after wildfires in south
OL,5,CSpain
OL,7,FAntonio Sanz, head of Andalusia's
OL,8,Femergency services, previously said
OL,9,Fthat authorities had completed post-
OL,10,Fmortem examinations and DNA samples
OL,11,Fwere collected to identify them.
OL,13,FAuthorities proactively evacuated
OL,14,F1,448 people from some 11 areas.
OL,16,FSpain has suffered frequent and severe
OL,17,Fheatwaves in recent years, with
OL,18,Ftemperatures often exceeding 40C.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
