OL,3,CTwo British hikers found alive but
OL,4,Cbadly burned after wildfires in south
OL,5,CSpain
OL,7,FIn June, Spain experienced several
OL,8,Fdays of record-setting heat, with more
OL,9,Fthan 1,000 excess deaths attributed to
OL,10,Fheat.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/7
